title: Bliss Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Pizza, International, Organic, Raw, Juice bar, Take-out, Mexican, Catering
description: Vegan cafe offering an varied food menu with dishes like kale & grains bowl and tempeh tacos as well coffee, smoothies and fresh juices. Relocated from 1035 Chorro St into this expanded space in early-2013. The inside has a cozy seating, and the back opens into more seating under large trees and by a creek.
